OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773324682
OL,3,C'We will not tolerate profiteering or
OL,4,Cunfair practices', Starmer warns
OL,5,Csuppliers
OL,7,FHe will hold meetings with political
OL,8,Fleaders, including First Minister
OL,9,FMichelle O'Neill and deputy First
OL,10,FMinister Emma Little-Pengelly, amid
OL,11,Fgrowing concerns over the impact the
OL,12,Fwar in the Middle East is having on
OL,13,Fenergy prices.
OL,15,FAround two-thirds of domestic
OL,16,Fproperties in Northern Ireland use
OL,17,Fhome heating oil.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
