OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773324682
OL,3,C'We will not tolerate profiteering or
OL,4,Cunfair practices', Starmer warns
OL,5,Csuppliers
OL,7,FGlobal oil prices have risen sharply
OL,8,Fin response to war in the Middle East,
OL,9,Fwith Iran launching strikes in
OL,10,Fresponse to attacks by the US and
OL,11,FIsrael, and home heating oil costs
OL,12,Fhave surged.
OL,14,FThe market in Northern Ireland, unlike
OL,15,Fgas and electricity, is unregulated.
OL,17,FTreasury minister Lord Livermore met
OL,18,Fwith some Northern Ireland MPs on
OL,19,FWednesday to discuss the issue.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
