PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773324682
OL,3,C'We will not tolerate profiteering or
OL,4,Cunfair practices', Starmer warns
OL,5,Csuppliers
OL,7,FThe Government said Sir Keir will use
OL,8,Fhis visit to Northern Ireland to
OL,9,F"highlight his relentless focus on
OL,10,Fcutting the cost of living for working
OL,11,Fpeople".
OL,13,FA statement said: "Recognising that
OL,14,Fthe majority of households in Northern
OL,15,FIreland rely on heating oil to heat
OL,16,Ftheir homes, the Prime Minister will
OL,17,Fsend the strong message to companies
OL,18,Fthat prices must be fair, transparent
OL,19,Fand justifiable, not inflated at the
OL,20,Fexpense of working people.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@GO]uD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
