PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773324682
OL,3,C'We will not tolerate profiteering or
OL,4,Cunfair practices', Starmer warns
OL,5,Csuppliers
OL,7,F"If companies hike prices without
OL,8,Fjustification, the Government will
OL,9,Fact, including through regulation."
OL,11,FThe Prime Minister said: "Global
OL,12,Finstability has real impacts on the
OL,13,Flives of working people across the UK,
OL,14,Fand I know families in Northern
OL,15,FIreland are worried about what the war
OL,16,Fin the Middle East could mean for
OL,17,Ftheir finances ` especially given so
OL,18,Fmany households rely on heating oil to
OL,19,Fheat their homes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@cO]sD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
