PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773324682
OL,3,C'We will not tolerate profiteering or
OL,4,Cunfair practices', Starmer warns
OL,5,Csuppliers
OL,7,F"Let me be clear, we will not tolerate
OL,8,Fprofiteering or unfair practices.
OL,10,F"If companies fleece customers or rip
OL,11,Fthem off, we will not hesitate to step
OL,12,Fin, and that includes on regulation.
OL,14,F"This Government stands with working
OL,15,Fpeople, no matter the headwinds.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
