OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773324682
OL,3,C'We will not tolerate profiteering or
OL,4,Cunfair practices', Starmer warns
OL,5,Csuppliers
OL,7,F"In Belfast I am spending my time
OL,8,Fmeeting not only the politicians
OL,9,Fmaking decisions in Stormont, but also
OL,10,Fthe people whose lives are shaped by
OL,11,Fconflicts abroad and the approach we
OL,12,Ftake at home."
OL,14,FThe Government has asked the
OL,15,FCompetition and Markets Authority to
OL,16,Flook at heating oil prices.
OL,18,FDuring the visit, the Prime Minister
OL,19,Fwill also meet with members of a local
OL,20,Fcommunity to discuss the cost of
OL,21,Fliving.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@NO]
